Package org.mybatis.spring.annotation

Class MapperScannerRegistrar

java.lang.Object
org.mybatis.spring.annotation.MapperScannerRegistrar
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.context.annotation.ImportBeanDefinitionRegistrar, org.springframework.context.ResourceLoaderAware
public class MapperScannerRegistrar
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.springframework.context.annotation.ImportBeanDefinitionRegistrar, org.springframework.context.ResourceLoaderAware
A ImportBeanDefinitionRegistrar to allow annotation configuration of MyBatis mapper scanning. Using an @Enable annotation allows beans to be registered via @Component configuration, whereas implementing BeanDefinitionRegistryPostProcessor will work for XML configuration.
Since:
1.2.0
Author:
Michael Lanyon, Eduardo Macarron, Putthiphong Boonphong
See Also:
MapperFactoryBean, ClassPathMapperScanner
